Let me inventory what data the algo gets each tick and what tutorial_T1800.py ignores.

Available Data per Tick
Source	Data	tutorial_T1800 uses?
order_depths	Best bid/ask prices	Only mid = (bid+ask)/2
order_depths	Bid/ask volumes (3 levels)	Ignored
order_depths	Spread width	Ignored
order_depths	Number of levels (2 vs 3)	Ignored
